This project is a rewrite of what was formerly known as "Open
Broadcaster Software", software originally designed for recording and
streaming live video content, efficiently.

i*86 systems are no longer supported.
See the SlackBuild for obs-studio-legacy for a version supporting 32bit.

This SlackBuild for 15.0 is pegged at version 30.1.2 since later
versions of obs-studio require ffmpg at least version 6.1 which is
not available in Slackware 15.0.

The SlackBuild uses a source tarball generated by the maintainer, since
those provided by upstream are incomplete. The script get-obs-studio.sh
is included here for anyone wishing to generate their own tarball.
